cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically the problem of removing motion blur. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a deep learning solution, which suggests it could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of synthetic data for training the model could also place it under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
